OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some rain
OL,6,Fbut this will soon clear east in the
OL,7,Fmorning. The rest of the day will be
OL,8,Fmainly dry but a few scattered showers
OL,9,Fwill develop, mostly over western
OL,10,FPerthshire and Stirling area.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright end to the day in
OL,13,Fthe east but cloudy with showers in
OL,14,Fthe west. The showers will continue in
OL,15,Fthe west overnight with a few reaching
OL,16,Fthe east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
